			<h2 class="excerpt">我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。</h2>
		<div class="detail">
				<h2>
	<span class="s1">Airbnb On River Thames by Airbnb&nbsp;</span> 
</h2>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1">Airbnb 近日推出了一个“水上漂浮屋”，位置是英国的泰晤士河上，屋子里设有一间客厅，两间卧室以及洗手间。而室外则有一座小花园，一个狗屋和一棵苹果树。这意味着，你甚至可以带上你的小狗去泰晤士河上发呆了。小屋将会从 5 月 22 日开始沿着泰晤士河一路漂流。</span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/6f7d21966449.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/1eb34ce9f58c.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/558e957096e4.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/7b87c2aac6fc.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/5d889278fbb9.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/dfb2208f2158.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/b0b746c99ee4.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/517e138a1702.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<h2>
	Light Phone by Joe Holler &amp; Kaiwei Tang
</h2>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1">Light Phone 是一款“反智能”的手机，它诞生于谷歌 30 Weeks 发起的设计师孵化器，来自艺术家 Joe Holler 和产品设计师 Kaiwei Tang。这款手机能做什么？答案是除了接打电话什么都不能。一次充电后可以满足 20 天左右的续航。“返璞归真”的手机不管从概念还是产品来讲都不少见，但能做的这么好看的还真不多。目前产品售价 100 美元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，感兴趣的话可以<a href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/thelightphone/the-light-phone" target="_blank">点击这里支持</a>。</span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201505/2e9af6fe43a7.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/464b30208a85.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/a65a14486f59.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/4a2fb1e1a620.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/e20c8b75d5d3.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/45c7b6b946c7.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/f748bb37b1da.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<h2>
	<span class="s1">hsbLABS by hsbCAD</span> 
</h2>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1">hsbCAD 工作室最近推出了一个可以帮助建筑设计师把平面设计方案变为 3D 立体模型的应用程序，名字叫做 “hsbLABS”。他们使用应用程序，将建筑草图分解成不同的部分，再通过 3D 打印机打印出来之后进行拼接。这款程序不需要其他的用具辅助，只需打印材料和颜料，便可以打印出立体的 3D 建筑模板。<a href="http://www.hsblabs.com/#target" target="_blank">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/af4c87c97756.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/6c9ec946295e.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/bead5178b594.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/c1fb582dfb48.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/9376f506eabb.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/52dc480976ab.jpg" alt="" /></span> 
</p>
<h2>
	<span class="s1">Italic Light by COORDINATION-berlin</span> 
</h2>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1">这款意大利灯由 COORDINATION-berlin 在 2015 年米兰设计周期间展出，灯的外部是一个大理石外壳，光束透过大理石内部放射出来，内置的是一个 LED 循环灯环，一个内置转换器和一个纺织电缆。灯具遵循极简主义设计风格，大理石的白和蓝色的配色看上去简单优雅。这是 <a href="http://www.coordination-berlin.com/?lang=en" target="_blank">COORDINATION-berlin 的官方主页</a>，感兴趣的话可以查看他们更多信息。</span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/8adf92c0ccdc.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/234060f54872.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/895bb2ba6356.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/3e5a63d82696.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/75659d03bb54.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/3fb81f695328.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<h2>
	Young at Heart by Disney &amp; Vans&nbsp;
</h2>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1">Disney 最近与 Vans 推出了一个新的联名系列，这个名为 “Young at Heart” 的系列在风格上和其名字一样动感十足，他们把 Disney 经典的卡通形象，如米老鼠，唐老鸭，维尼小熊等印制在了 Vans 经典的“一脚蹬”以及书包，帆布鞋，袜子等产品上面，营造出浓浓的夏日可爱风。这个联名系列将在 6 月正式登陆 Vans 全球指定店铺。</span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/12d124dacd05.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/b6b0c015247a.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/56a2cbb1b9d4.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/9526b180cb56.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/15fcf914e9be.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<h2>
	<span class="s1">Hot Milk Lab by Sebastian Bergne&nbsp;</span> 
</h2>
<p class="p2">
	<span class="s1"></span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1">设计师 Sebastian Bergne 最近推出了一个“迷你实验室”，方便人们制作各种饮料。其中 Hot Milk Lab 专门方便人们在热牛奶里面加入各种配料，制作出不同风味的饮料。Sebastian Bergne 的这一套实验室由木制的托盘和不同型号的玻璃瓶，酒精灯以及托盘组成，烧牛奶的玻璃瓶中放置了一个温度计，可以方便使用者调节温度。</span> 
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<span class="s1"><img src="/uploads/image/201505/4a61da8a91c1.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/7b44c8d2c5fb.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/2075b06cde71.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/c43bbb5b17a6.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/a8578fcc9dac.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/45a3e51e4c14.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/2a6a655bb597.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/image/201505/7a4f93595a08.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span>
</p>
<p class="p1">
	<br />
</p>
		</div>
	</div>
